CRM System Security Documentation

1. Authentication & Authorization
- User login required for all sensitive operations
- Session management with secure tokens
- Role-based access control (Admin/User)
- Permission checks for every API endpoint

2. Data Protection
- Passwords stored securely (hashing recommended)
- Sensitive data (user info, audit logs) protected in database
- Access to data restricted by user roles and permissions

3. API Security
- All API endpoints validate user session and permissions
- CORS enabled for safe cross-origin requests
- Input validation to prevent SQL injection, XSS, and other attacks
- Error handling to avoid information leakage

4. Audit Logging
- Every critical action (login, lead change, user update, report upload) logged in audit table
- Security audit table API for admin review
- Logs include user, action, resource, timestamp, and status

5. File Upload Security
- Only allowed file types (e.g., PDF for reports, images for user photos)
- File size and content type validation
- Uploaded files stored in protected directories

6. Session & Cookie Security
- Session tokens used for authentication
- Secure cookie handling (recommended: HttpOnly, Secure flags)
- Session expiration and invalidation on logout

7. Error & Exception Handling
- API returns generic error messages for unauthorized/forbidden access
- Detailed errors logged for admin review, not exposed to users

8. Static & Template Security
- Static files served from dedicated directory
- Templates rendered with context sanitization

9. Database Security
- Direct DB access restricted to backend only
- Connection credentials stored securely
- Regular database backups and access monitoring

10. Future Security Enhancements
- Two-factor authentication (2FA)
- Encryption for sensitive fields
- Security audit dashboard
- Automated vulnerability scanning

Summary:
Smart CRM System me authentication, authorization, audit logging, file validation, session management, error handling, and data protection ke security layers implemented hain. Ye system business data ko unauthorized access, tampering, aur misuse se protect karta hai.

Agar kisi specific security feature ka detail chahiye ho, bata sakte hain.